public record Customer(int customerId, String customerName, String address, String postalCode, String phone, Timestamp createDate, String createdBy, Timestamp lastUpdate, String lastUpdateBy, FirstLevelDivision division) extends Record
A data carrier class that contains database CRUD operations as static methods for the customers table. A row returned from the table is packaged as a Customer data-transfer-like object.
